":237888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70d943e48300d2fa053797e5bb0016dcf926d517","tid":1204123,"uid":139228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:21:47.000Z","msg":"仔嗌咩好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"有人揸我look鳩"},{"pid":"f0cd08a7e58234f22f1c939580629c1a7cf6c867","tid":1204123,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"1. 詢問理由 (警察講到個罪行出嚟都唔夠，仲要有清晰原因)<br />\n2. 可行使權利，要求<span style=\"color: red;\">到警署搜身</span><br />\n3. 被警察即場搜身，<span style=\"color: red;\">搜身後已可</span><span style=\"color: red;\">離去</span><br />\n4. 警察無權要求市民「一字排開」等待，市民可反問警察是否要作出<span style=\"color: red;\">拘捕</span>，否則便要<span style=\"color: red;\">放人</span><br />\n5. 有需要可找法律義務支援求助<br />\n6. 守望相助，幫其他人拍低過程<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n律師：警察無權隨意搜身   市民拍片保護自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203934</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"97a4acd6ad6aa7d88662788d329968a2ac78b900","tid":1204123,"uid":237888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:40:31.000Z","msg":"大叫雞姦"}]}